    <item>
      <title>印度取消部分大米出口税以提高竞争力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/india-scraps-tax-on-some-rice-exports-to-boost-competitiveness</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度取消了对非巴斯马蒂蒸谷米出口的限制，此举可能增强该国在国际市场上的竞争力，并在当前收获季节提高当地农民的收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/india-scraps-tax-on-some-rice-exports-to-boost-competitiveness</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 18:43:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CFTC 主席 Behnam 表示，CFTC 将对选举博彩平台进行监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/cftc-to-police-bet-platforms-but-would-rather-not-chair-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国商品期货交易委员会主席罗斯汀·贝纳姆（Rostin Behnam）在周二接受彭博电视采访时表示，尽管该委员会竭尽全力想要消灭注册的政治衍生品市场，但它仍将对其进行监管。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/cftc-to-police-bet-platforms-but-would-rather-not-chair-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 18:26:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EQT 董事长称地缘政治是首要担忧，而非利率上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/eqt-chair-says-geopolitics-risk-is-no-1-worry-not-higher-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[EQT AB 董事长康尼·琼森 (Conni Jonsson) 表示，目前世界的地缘政治紧张局势比借贷成本上升的问题更令其公司担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/eqt-chair-says-geopolitics-risk-is-no-1-worry-not-higher-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 17:35:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Gatemore 寻求回购瑞士手表并在美国上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/gatemore-pushes-watches-of-switzerland-for-buyback-us-listing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Gatemore Capital Management 已入股瑞士钟表集团有限公司 (Watches of Switzerland Group Plc)，并要求这家奢侈手表零售商积极回购股票，并考虑在美国上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/gatemore-pushes-watches-of-switzerland-for-buyback-us-listing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 17:28:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>水电供应减少 巴西考虑在 2025 年初进口液化天然气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/brazil-mulls-lng-imports-into-early-2025-as-hydro-levels-shrink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于持续干旱天气威胁水力发电，巴西的天然气买家正在询问第一季度全球天然气的潜在购买量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/brazil-mulls-lng-imports-into-early-2025-as-hydro-levels-shrink</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 15:54:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
